thread.title_full: BRIEF-Grand Rounds secures $55 million in Series C financing | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Grand Rounds secures $55 million in Series C financing
text:
Aug 20 Grand Rounds:
* Grand Rounds says has secured $55 million in Series C financing
* Grand Rounds says will use the funds to expand its technology, care team and analytics platform
* Grand Rounds says the round brings grand rounds' total funding to $106 million
